nextNumber  Help
The next number to be assigned. This is a number that has NOT yet been used. Clients will usually increment this value by one each time an order number is needed. However, if a client needs a batch of multiple orders numbers this value may be incremented by some larger unit (e.g.: 10).
  		integer required
 
lockVersion  Help
